  "prompt": "Which is a good inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center near Coffee County AL?",
  "response": "Finding the right inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center is a crucial step toward recovery. Near Coffee County, Alabama, several reputable facilities can help you or a loved one on the path to sobriety. Here are a few options to consider:\n\n### 1. **Dothan Recovery Center**\nLocated in Dothan, just a short drive from Coffee County, Dothan Recovery Center offers comprehensive inpatient treatment programs. They provide individualized care plans, therapy sessions, and support groups to address substance abuse issues.\n\n- **Address:** [Insert Address]\n- **Phone:** [Insert Phone Number]\n- **Website:** [Insert Website]\n\n### 2. **Southeast Health Systems**\nAlso based in Dothan, Southeast Health Systems specializes in both substance abuse and mental health treatment. Their inpatient programs include medical detoxification, residential therapy, and aftercare planning.\n\n- **Address:** [Insert Address]\n- **Phone:** [Insert Phone Number]\n- **Website:** [Insert Website]\n\n### 3. **Enterprise Behavioral Health**\nLocated in Enterprise, this facility provides inpatient treatment for addiction and co-occurring mental health disorders. Their multidisciplinary team offers personalized treatment plans to support long-term recovery.\n\n- **Address:** [Insert Address]\n- **Phone:** [Insert Phone Number]\n- **Website:** [Insert Website]\n\n### 4. **Debra's Detox & Rehabilitation**\nWhile primarily focused on detoxification, Debra's also offers inpatient rehab services in the nearby region. They emphasize a holistic approach, incorporating physical, emotional, and spiritual healing.\n\n- **Address:** [Insert Address]\n- **Phone:** [Insert Phone Number]\n- **Website:** [Insert Website]\n\n### Additional Resources\n\n- **SAMHSA Treatment Locator:** The Substance Abuse and Mental Health Services Administration (SAMHSA) provides a [treatment facility locator](https://findtreatment.samhsa.gov/) that can help you find accredited rehab centers based on your specific needs and location.\n  \n- **Consult Healthcare Professionals:** It's advisable to consult with a healthcare provider or a counselor who can offer personalized recommendations based on individual circumstances.\n\n### Important Considerations\n\n- **Accreditation and Licensing:** Ensure the facility is accredited by recognized organizations and holds the necessary licenses to operate.\n  \n- **Treatment Approaches:** Different centers may use varying treatment methodologies (e.g., Cognitive Behavioral Therapy, 12-Step Programs). Consider which approach aligns best with your preferences.\n  \n- **Insurance and Costs:** Verify whether the center accepts your insurance plan and understand the costs involved, including any out-of-pocket expenses.\n\n- **Aftercare Support:** Recovery doesn't end after inpatient treatment. Look for centers that offer robust aftercare services to support long-term sobriety.\n\nChoosing the right rehab center is a personal decision, and it's essential to research thoroughly and possibly visit facilities to find the best fit for your needs. Wishing you strength and success on your journey to recovery.",
